}}</ref>
and the President<U+2019>s Award 2007 from The [[Society for Technical Communication]] "for demonstrating that effective and understandable technical communication, when coupled with passion and vision, has the power to educate<U+2014>and change<U+2014>the world."<ref name="presidentsaward">{{cite web
