For Gore's wide-reaching efforts to draw the world<U+2019>s attention to the dangers of global warming which is centerpieced in the film, Al Gore, along with the [[Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change]] (IPCC), won the 2007 [[Nobel Peace Prize]].<ref name="nobelpeaceprize">{{cite web
